        <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:1;23:13" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-contraints-redefine-content-model.dita">She creates a .mod file using the following naming conventions:
              <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrc="filepath:1;24:25" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-contraints-redefine-content-model.dita"><varname class="+ topic/keyword sw-d/varname " xtrc="varname:1;24:34" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-contraints-redefine-content-model.dita">qualifer</varname><varname class="+ topic/keyword sw-d/varname " xtrc="varname:2;24:61" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-contraints-redefine-content-model.dita">Tagname</varname>Constraint.mod</filepath>,
